	   <tr><td colspan=2>hey there you clerics! im an 18 lvl rogue and i have a bone to pick. now, in order to safe fall and get skill gain, you do NOT need to inflict damage one yourself. only a dumb rogue would take his life down to 2 bubs safefalling because hes attempting to hard of a fall. when i practice i take about a total of 7dmg and get about 10skill gains, so a nice light heal wouldn't be so much to ask. therefore, its rude to make your life go that low, no necessarily to practice a great skill in the downtime.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
